{"ID":"20231008213710-fqer7v8","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"1f69d","id":"20231008213710-fqer7v8","title":"如何学习","updated":"20231008221828"},"Children":[{"ID":"20231008213710-cib0upr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231008213710-cib0upr","updated":"20231008221828"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"学习主要分为三个阶段，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"style":"font-size: 19px; background-color: var(--b3-card-info-background); color: var(--b3-card-info-color);"},"TextMarkType":"strong text","TextMarkTextContent":"前期的学习主要偏向基础知识，比如 MySQL、Redis、设计模式、计算机网络、操作系统、语言栈相关知识等，为了能系统学习这些知识，我会购买经典的书籍，每本书至少读两遍。"},{"Type":"NodeKramdownSpanIAL","Data":"{: style=\"font-size: 19px; background-color: var(--b3-card-info-background); color: var(--b3-card-info-color);\"}"}]},{"ID":"20231008220224-tqzlexb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231008220224-tqzlexb","updated":"20231008220449"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"因为书籍需要兼顾大多读者，所以知识面很全，但是深度不够"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，因此我会去选择买一些极客时间的课程，比如林晓斌的《MySQL 实战 45 讲》、郝林的《Go 语言核心 36 讲》，来弥补书籍深度的不足。"}]},{"ID":"20231008221821-d0bj0mf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20231008221821-d0bj0mf","updated":"20231008221822"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"第二个阶段就是知识广度的学习，这部分内容主要包括消息队列、微服务、注册中心、配置中心、RPC、DDD、高并发、容器等，我主要的学习渠道是博客，然后也会买一些极客时间的课程。"}]}]}